Enactment of the CANADA PORT AUTHORITY ENVIRONMENTAL ASSESSMENT REGULATIONS
which prescribe the manner in which environmental assessments are to be
conducted by the 18 Port Corporations and Commissions that are to be
continued as Canada Port Authorities under the Canada Marine Act.
